<DocsLayout title={title}>
<h1>Video Editing</h1>
<p>Edit an existing video with a text prompt using <code>POST /v1/videos/edits</code>. Supply the source video in the <code>video</code> field. The operation is asynchronous — poll the returned task ID for completion, same as video generation.</p>
<pre><code>{`curl -X POST http://localhost:18645/v1/videos/edits \
  -H "Authorization: Bearer $API_KEY" \
  -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
  -d '{
    "video": "https://example.com/source.mp4",
    "prompt": "Add cinematic color grading"
  }'`}</code></pre>
</DocsLayout>
